🧾 PROMETHEUS ALERTMANAGER
✅ Полная установка и настройка (Ubuntu)
✅ 1. Установка Alertmanager (OFFICIAL)
cd /opt

sudo wget https://github.com/prometheus/alertmanager/releases/download/v0.31.1/alertmanager-0.31.1.linux-amd64.tar.gz

sudo tar -xvzf alertmanager-0.31.1.linux-amd64.tar.gz
sudo mv alertmanager-0.31.1.linux-amd64 alertmanager
✅ 2. Установка бинарников
sudo cp /opt/alertmanager/alertmanager /usr/local/bin/
sudo cp /opt/alertmanager/amtool /usr/local/bin/

Проверка:

alertmanager --version
✅ 3. Пользователь сервиса
sudo useradd --no-create-home --shell /bin/false alertmanager
✅ 4. Каталоги
sudo mkdir /etc/alertmanager
sudo mkdir /var/lib/alertmanager
✅ 5. Конфигурация Alertmanager
sudo nano /etc/alertmanager/alertmanager.yml
Минимальный WORKING CONFIG
global:
  resolve_timeout: 5m

route:
  receiver: default

receivers:
- name: default
Проверка YAML
amtool check-config /etc/alertmanager/alertmanager.yml

✅ должно быть:

SUCCESS
✅ 6. Права доступа
sudo chown -R alertmanager:alertmanager /etc/alertmanager
sudo chown -R alertmanager:alertmanager /var/lib/alertmanager
✅ 7. Systemd service
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/alertmanager.service
✅ Production service
[Unit]
Description=Alertmanager
After=network.target

[Service]
User=alertmanager
Group=alertmanager
Type=simple
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/alertmanager \
--config.file=/etc/alertmanager/alertmanager.yml \
--storage.path=/var/lib/alertmanager \
--web.listen-address=:9093 \
--cluster.listen-address=:9095

Restart=always

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
✅ 8. Запуск
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable alertmanager
sudo systemctl start alertmanager
✅ 9. Проверка
systemctl status alertmanager

должно быть:

Active: active (running)

Порты:

ss -tulpn | grep alert
9093 → Web UI
9095 → Cluster
✅ 10. Web UI
http://SERVER_IP:9093
🚨 11. Подключение к Prometheus

Открыть:

sudo nano /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml

Добавить:

alerting:
  alertmanagers:
    - static_configs:
        - targets:
          - localhost:9093

Перезапуск:

sudo systemctl restart prometheus
🚨 12. Alert Rules (пример)
sudo nano /etc/prometheus/alerts.yml
NGINX DOWN ALERT
groups:
- name: nginx-alerts
  rules:

  - alert: NginxDown
    expr: up{job="nginx"} == 0
    for: 1m
    labels:
      severity: critical
    annotations:
      summary: "NGINX DOWN"
      description: "Instance {{ $labels.instance }} is DOWN"

Добавить в prometheus.yml:

rule_files:
  - /etc/prometheus/alerts.yml

Restart:

sudo systemctl restart prometheus
✅ 13. Проверка Alert

Открыть:

http://SERVER_IP:9090/alerts

Остановить nginx:

sudo systemctl stop nginx

Через ~1 минуту:

✅ ALERT FIRING

